snippet.title: Summer's Gone - Season 1 - Ambient Trailer #1 (2023)
snippet.description:
SG on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2240150/Summers_Gone__Season_1/
SG on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SummersGone

Watch the video in 4k, or it will look muddy due to YouTube's strong compression.

Summer's Gone is a story-focused Visual Novel for adults. 

The game is going to release in early to mid 2023 on Steam when Chapter 5 is finished. 

Play Chapter 1 to Chapter 4.5 already here: https://www.patreon.com/SummersGone



Music: The Intangible - Qualia
